// Ninja-faction lair — the Shadow Dojo. A wide horizontal room
// tucked above the Pirate Cove (worldY = -800). Two doors: one back
// to the central hub, one across into the Mockingbird boss arena.
//
// Storyline: ninjas and pirates loathe each other on principle, but
// the Mockingbird stole a kata from the dojo and a hoard from the
// cove, so each crew has agreed to run their own door into the boss
// room. The leader (Shadow Oni) will broker a one-engagement truce;
// the duelist will trash-talk pirates for the entire conversation.
//
// Layout (1280 wide × 640 tall — same shell shape as the cove so
// both faction rooms read as siblings on the world map):
//
//   +---------------------------------------------------+  y = 0
//   | ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒ ceiling ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒  |
//   |                                                   |
//   |        ░░ training beam ░░                        |
//   |                              ░░ training beam ░░  |
//   |                                                   |
//   |  [hub door]                          [arena door] |
//   | ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒  | y = 608 (floor)
//   +---------------------------------------------------+
//
// Music: `ninja_guild_shadow_kata` — already registered in
// `crates/ambition_actors/assets/ambition/sandbox.ron`. The boss
// track swap to `how_to_kill_a_mockingbird` happens when the player
// crosses the loading zone into the arena, identical to the cove.

